      "Article.java": {
        "text": "/*\n * Represents a news article\n */\npublic class Article {\n    \n  private String company1;\n  private String company2;\n\n  /*\n   * Sets company1 and company2 to the specified names\n   */\n  public Article(String company1, String company2) {\n    this.company1 = company1;\n    this.company2 = company2;\n  }\n\n  /*\n   * Compares the two company names using compareTo() and returns the result\n   */\n  public int compareCompanies() {\n    /* ----------------------------------- TO DO -----------------------------------\n     * ✅ Use compareTo() to compare company1 and company2.\n     * Return the result of the comparison as an integer.\n     * -----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n     */\n\n    \n\n    return 0;\n  }\n}\n",
